/*------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  Purpose:     Override standard ADM method
  Notes:       
------------------------------------------------------------------------------*/
  
  /* Code placed here will execute PRIOR to standard behavior. */
  RUN valid-sman (0) NO-ERROR.
  IF ERROR-STATUS:ERROR THEN RETURN NO-APPLY.

  RUN valid-s-pct (0) NO-ERROR.
